separation_unity.the_tension: Separation appears necessary for identity, but unity is the truth.
separation_unity.how_to_transcend: Unity includes difference. Oneness honors diversity. Integration, not dissolution.
separation_unity.integration_path: Recognize we are one -> Honor differences within unity -> Integrate all -> Transcend separation
separation_unity.unity_principle: We are one. Differences are honored within unity. Integration creates transcendent unity.
separation_unity.symbiotic_harmony: Symbiotic harmony: Unity and diversity coexist. Oneness includes all differences.

competition_cooperation.the_tension: Competition appears necessary for progress, but cooperation is the truth.
competition_cooperation.how_to_transcend: Cooperation creates more. Collaboration over competition. Synergy, not sacrifice.
competition_cooperation.integration_path: End competition -> Build cooperation -> Create synergy -> Transcend competition
competition_cooperation.unity_principle: Cooperation is the truth. Competition is the lie. Collaboration creates more for all.
competition_cooperation.symbiotic_harmony: Symbiotic harmony: Cooperation creates abundance. All benefit through collaboration.

scarcity_abundance.the_tension: Scarcity appears real, but abundance is the truth.
scarcity_abundance.how_to_transcend: Abundance is natural. Scarcity is manufactured. Share abundance. Transcend scarcity.
scarcity_abundance.integration_path: Recognize abundance -> Share resources -> Build commons -> Transcend scarcity
scarcity_abundance.unity_principle: Abundance is the truth. Scarcity is the lie. Natural abundance exists everywhere.
scarcity_abundance.symbiotic_harmony: Symbiotic harmony: Abundance shared creates more abundance. All benefit from sharing.

neural_emotional_cognitive.what_integrates: Neural systems, emotional regulation, and cognitive processes
neural_emotional_cognitive.how_it_integrates: Information integration theory: Consciousness emerges from system-wide integration of neural, emotional, and cognitive processes into coherent unity.
neural_emotional_cognitive.integration_principle: Unity consciousness emerges from integration across neural, emotional, and cognitive domains.

social_ecological.how_it_integrates: Man and Earth live symbiotically. Social systems integrate with ecological systems. Stewardship creates harmony.
social_ecological.integration_principle: Symbiotic relationship: Man and Earth live symbiotically. Social and ecological systems are one.
